36:10.356 --> 36:12.817
The stuff that nobody is
supposed to hear, I hear that stuff.

36:12.858 --> 36:16.612
You know what I'm saying ?
I can hear what women think.

36:16.653 --> 36:19.698
Can you ? Good, 'cause that's not
