and not down my blouse.

37:43.817 --> 37:45.985
- Nick, what did you come up with ?
- Me ?

37:46.069 --> 37:48.738
What did I come up with ?
[ Chuckles ]

37:48.821 --> 37:51.490
He's so wired.

37:51.574 --> 37:53.492
Mostly...
[ Clears Throat ]

37:53.576 --> 37:56.203
