working on it, and it's evolving.

38:21.768 --> 38:26.105
Anybody interested in an idea
involving the Swedish bikini team ?

38:26.147 --> 38:28.441
I do know them all
personally.

38:28.524 --> 38:31.777
- Oh, what an idiot.
-Jerk, grow up already.

38:31.861 --> 38:34.029
- What a pig.
- You are so foul.

38:34.113 --> 38:38.700
