for more money. Gina ?

38:38.784 --> 38:42.412
I spent the night trying to figure
out how to sell Advil just to women.

38:42.495 --> 38:45.540
You know what ?
You should sell it to women like me.

38:45.623 --> 38:47.583
[Giggles]

38:47.667 --> 38:50.336
I take it every time
I need to fake a headache.

38:50.419 --> 38:52.505
Works like a charm.

38:52.588 --> 38:55.549
I-I got a great one.
It just came to me.

38:55.632 --> 38:57.718
- Do you mind if I interrupt, Dina ?
- Sure, go ahead.

38:57.801 --> 38:59.803
I hate that
you've seen me naked.

39:02.097 --> 39:04.807
[ Chuckles ]
All right.

39:04.891 --> 39:07.101
So, we're in a bedroom,
the lights are out.

39:07.185 --> 39:09.145
There's a woman in bed,
and she's taking an Advil.

39:09.187 --> 39:15.109
Her husband suggestively
rubs her back, and we say, ''Advil.

39:15.150 --> 39:17.653
''So mild and gentle,
you can take it...

39:17.736 --> 39:21.156
even when you're
faking a headache.''

39:21.239 --> 39:23.158
[ Laughter ]

39:23.241 --> 39:27.829
Woman turns to her husband and says,
''Not tonight, I need an Advil. ''

39:28.913 --> 39:32.041
- He's back.
- [ Laughs ]

39:33.626 --> 39:37.921
What ? Come on. That doesn't
reach women on a personal level ?

39:38.005 --> 39:40.757
- No.
- Women do that, don't they ?

39:40.841 --> 39:42.342
- I don't.
- No ?

39:42.425 --> 39:47.638
Sue Cranston, you've done that,
haven't you ? Faked a headache to--

39:47.722 --> 39:51.517
No, Nick, I haven't.
Thanks for asking.

39:51.600 --> 39:54.019
No, wait, wait, wait.
Be honest now.

39:54.061 --> 39:57.606
