feeling me up in front of my father.

40:58.603 --> 41:01.814
Don't think anything. The outlook
wasn't good for the Mudville Nine.

41:01.897 --> 41:04.441
- The score was four to two.
- Oh, shit. Where's my bra ?

41:04.525 --> 41:07.069
- Where is it ?
- Oh, God.

41:08.779 --> 41:11.364
Oh, God !

41:11.448 --> 41:14.951
Okay, look. Everybody
just needs to chill out here.

41:15.034 --> 41:18.538
