Just get your stuff... and move on.

41:18.621 --> 41:20.665
Come on, man. Relax.

41:20.748 --> 41:22.833
- How old are you ?
- I just turned 1 8.

41:22.917 --> 41:24.877
Well, she's 1 5.
She was 10 five years ago.

41:24.960 --> 41:26.879
You know what I'm saying,
stud ? Now get out.

41:26.962 --> 41:30.048
Dad ! [ Thinking ] We're going
to the prom. Don't ruin it.

41:30.132 --> 41:33.510
- You're not going with this punk.
- How did you know about prom ?

41:33.551 --> 41:35.511
Look, I don't know.
Mom told me, all right ?

41:35.553 --> 41:37.764
It's not gonna happen
because he's too old for you.

41:37.847 --> 41:41.058
I know what boys want, and he's not
getting it from my daughter. Door.

41:41.142 --> 41:44.019
Your daughter ?
Suddenly, I'm your daughter.

41:44.061 --> 41:47.105
- How am I related to this asshole ?
- Another one.

41:47.189 --> 41:51.568
- I want Mom.
- Look, l'm just gonna take off.

41:51.651 --> 41:54.529
- l'm real sorry about this.
- Save it.

41:54.612 --> 41:57.073
That's mine.

41:57.156 --> 42:01.327
Where-- Where are you--

42:01.369 --> 42:03.954
[ Sighs ]

42:04.038 --> 42:05.956
Great day.

42:06.039 --> 42:08.000
[Thunderclap]

42:08.125 --> 42:12.045
Okay, l'm not losing
my mind.

42:12.128 --> 42:14.756
- I'm already losing my mind.

42:14.839 --> 42:17.508
- This will work. It's gotta work.

42:17.592 --> 42:20.886
-This has gotta work. Shit. Perfect.

42:56.586 --> 42:58.463
- [ Screams ]
- [Thunderclap]

43:07.179 --> 43:09.097
[Thunderclap]

43:21.734 --> 43:25.946
Come on !
Do your thing !

43:26.029 --> 43:28.115
Turn me into me again !

43:32.494 --> 43:34.871
[ Hair Dryer Whirring ]

44:12.781 --> 44:16.159
Oh, good, I'm not dead.

44:16.242 --> 44:18.327
[ Panting ]
Oh, please !

44:18.411 --> 44:21.455
Please, please, please.
Tell me I got rid of it.

44:21.539 --> 44:24.708
- [ Beeping ]
- Please be a woman. Please.

44:24.792 --> 44:28.420
- For what city, please ?
- You couldn't do me a favor...

44:28.462 --> 44:31.089
and think of your favorite color
or TV program, could you ?

44:31.172 --> 44:33.591
For what city, please ?

44:33.675 --> 44:35.635
[ Sighs ]

44:36.928 --> 44:39.889
Flo ? Hey, Flo !

44:39.972 --> 44:41.932
