into buying that lamp on eBay.

47:35.675 --> 47:38.678
- How much was it going for ?
- How much was what going for ?

47:38.761 --> 47:40.930
The lamp on eBay.

47:44.224 --> 47:48.145
Oh, I see. That's good.
Very clever.

47:48.186 --> 47:52.565
- Dr. Skolnick, please.
- You don't believe me. Try another.

47:52.649 --> 47:54.943
Go on. Pick a number.
Give it a whirl. Any number.

47:54.984 --> 47:56.986
Okay. A number
between one and--

47:57.070 --> 47:59.530
- A million. Why not ?
- One and a million.

47:59.614 --> 48:02.032
All right.

48:02.116 --> 48:04.034
Mm.

48:04.118 --> 48:07.329
644,998-- 99-- 90.

48:08.413 --> 48:11.082
Wanna make a decision here ?

48:11.166 --> 48:14.502
- Oy vay!
- Oh, you can say that again.

48:14.586 --> 48:17.713
- I didn't say anything.
- Doesn't mean I didn't hear it.

48:17.797 --> 48:22.426
Okay. Okay. Let's say--
Let's say I do believe you.

48:22.510 --> 48:26.138
- Yeah.
- You can hear what women think.

48:26.221 --> 48:29.683
Even though I'm a grown
woman of... [ Thinking ] 51 .

48:29.766 --> 48:33.561
- 47.
- Oh, my lips are sealed.

48:33.645 --> 48:36.564
Holy crap !
Oh, forgive me.

48:36.648 --> 48:39.692
- That's all right.
- But this is phenomenal.

48:39.775 --> 48:42.444
- You can hear inside my head.
- Yes.

48:42.528 --> 48:44.947
Why would you want to get rid
of such a brilliant gift ?

48:45.030 --> 48:47.950
Well, for starters,

48:48.033 --> 48:50.911
almost every woman I know
thinks I'm an asshole.

48:50.994 --> 48:54.330
- What I thought when I met you.
- Doc, give me a break here.

48:54.414 --> 48:57.250
Mr. Marshall, you might
find this a little unorthodox,

48:57.333 --> 48:59.168
but would you mind
awfully if I smoked ?

48:59.252 --> 49:01.629
- No, no, I understand.
- Thank you. Thank you so much.

49:12.889 --> 49:15.183
[ Coughs ]

49:15.266 --> 49:18.102
Let's try to look at
the up side of this, shall we ?

49:18.186 --> 49:22.106
You know, Freud died at age 83
still asking one question,

49:22.189 --> 49:24.108
''What do women want ?''

49:24.191 --> 49:28.362
Wouldn't it be strange and wonderful
if you were the one man on Earth...

49:28.445 --> 49:30.947
finally able to answer
that question ?

49:31.031 --> 49:33.533
Listen to me, Nick.
Something extraordinary...

49:33.616 --> 49:36.077
and I think miraculous
has happened to you.

49:36.160 --> 49:39.413
