50:47.267 --> 50:49.936
Hey, Nick, how's it going ?

50:49.978 --> 50:54.440
Lola, my love.
I can't take no for an answer.

50:54.524 --> 50:57.443
- About what ?
- About what ?

50:57.527 --> 50:59.946
[ Chuckles ]
About us.

50:59.987 --> 51:05.200
Just don't hurt me, Nick.
I've been hurt too many times.

51:05.284 --> 51:08.620
I know how hard it is
to go out with someone new.

51:08.662 --> 51:11.206
I mean, there's always
that fear of,

51:11.289 --> 51:13.708
well, getting hurt.

51:13.792 --> 51:16.794
- At least that's how I feel inside.
- You do, really ?

51:16.878 --> 51:20.548
- [ Sighs ] All the time.
- Me, too, all the time.

51:20.631 --> 51:22.800
Let's just take it slow
and see how it goes.

51:22.883 --> 51:25.511
Slow is good.

51:25.594 --> 51:27.512
Slow is really good.

51:27.596 --> 51:31.099
- Yeah.
