51:31.182 --> 51:34.477
So, you don't think I'm gay ?
You're saying you never said that ?

51:34.561 --> 51:36.813
- I never said that.
- Doesn't mean you didn't think it.

51:36.854 --> 51:39.023
Is it the hair ? The highlights
happen to be natural.

51:39.106 --> 51:41.525
- Morgan, I have a meeting.
- You don't think I'm overpaid?

51:41.609 --> 51:45.904
- You never said that.
- I don't think I ever said that.

51:45.988 --> 51:48.156
Okay.

51:48.240 --> 51:50.158
[ Thinking ]
Who has he been talking to ?

51:50.242 --> 51:52.160
- Morning.
- Morning.

51:52.243 --> 51:54.162
Well, then check your E-mail.
I sent it over--

51:54.245 --> 51:56.289
Hi, Annie.
How's the boyfriend in Israel ?

51:56.372 --> 51:58.416
I want to thank you
for picking up that wine.

51:58.499 --> 52:00.960
