52:10.093 --> 52:13.680
That's right, guys, don't help.
Just walk right past me.

52:13.763 --> 52:15.682
Why don't you step on
my hands, you big--

52:15.765 --> 52:19.185
- Here you go. How you doing ?
- Oh.

52:19.268 --> 52:23.022
Oh, fine.
Thank you, Mr. Marshall.

52:23.105 --> 52:26.024
- You're welcome, um--
