52:28.568 --> 52:30.737
Yeah, sure.

52:30.820 --> 52:32.739
Heavy.

52:35.200 --> 52:38.369
What do you know ?
There is life on this planet.

52:43.999 --> 52:46.585
Breakfast Tuesday sounds great.
Absolutely.

52:46.668 --> 52:50.255
Thanks for the info.
